race.description: Ladbrokes Launceston Cup Wed 25 Feb Maiden Plate
race.comment: RUSHONOVA (13) and prepared well and made an encouraging debut when placing second over 1200m at this track. Draws low and keeps the 3kg claim. Strips fitter and can go one better. BAD ALIBI (12) peaks off narrow defeats here and led heavily bet last time. Has a 3kg claim but the gate is a little awkward. Could be too good regardless. WHO'S IN DEV (14) resumes and placed here at a short quote before the spell. Brings a big trial win from Longford and will be naturally improved. She's also rates a decent chance. TIGERS ON TOP (9) did well off a wide gate to find a place here first-up. Will have to do it the hard way again but keeps the 2kg claim and she may have turned the corner.
